{"tid":1887251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美心向惜食堂捐贈10萬個口罩、4萬張套餐券及一批食品轉送有需要長者！","createTime":"2020-02-19T11:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T15:57:41.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7aaea71ca421350451f5f51e2d2118331cb6c7","tid":1887251,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32785fa18bf3ccddaf156ec2f91dbcb5c8d328a1","tid":1887251,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情持續，不少企業或機構續免費派發防疫用品予有需要人士。惜食堂亦將在派發食物期間，同時將所獲得的防疫用品轉贈予服務使用者，以解其燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n惜食堂指出，一直致力為長者送上溫飽，亦希望照顧長者們不同的生活需要。在新冠肺炎肆虐期間，長者除需要食物援助外，還要面對缺乏防疫用品的問題。<br />\n<br />\n而該會今日獲美心集團捐贈10萬個口罩、4萬張套餐券及一批食品，故會將這批物資陸續送給有需要的長者。同時，亦會透過超過70間慈善機構伙伴，轉贈到其服務使用者手上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2568878/?=mcdfbez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2568878%2F%3F%3Dmcdfbez&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5ANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=cc649c9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2568878/?=mcdfbez</a>"},{"pid":"cf735ed9c50c3ffd8ae296a30bee81be46fa8442","tid":1887251,"uid":31787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"屌美心老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa166db0ebfd69675f97ad67639dbe47ce53c17e","tid":1887251,"uid":37957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母套餐券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4305ab9ec29976ac987c227a98a15da5989f8b6a","tid":1887251,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"好心啦<br />\n咁大個集團咁遲先得嗰十萬仲好意思俾人知<br />\n以為自己好能幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bdb672b858ea032ffaa1db4db5a67077701207","t